  "title": "Audit Partner",
  "description": "<p>· Carry out audit work, in accordance with Singapore Standards on Auditing, of companies in various industries</p><p>· Manage a portfolio of audit clients including control of billings and cash collections.</p><p>· Plan staff assignments</p><p>· Mentor and develop staff including provide training to staff, both on the job and through more formal training programs</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>· Must be professionally qualified (Degree, ACCA or equivalent)</p><p>· Minimum 5 years audit experience with at least 1 year in supervisory role</p><p>· Staff management experience including mentoring, counseling, appraising and recruiting.</p><p>· Excellent communications and interpersonal skills</p><p>· Strong technical knowledge</p><p>· Good team player</p><p>· Highly motivated and with strong desire to progress</p><p>· CA Singapore, preferred</p>",
